Package se.hig.dvg329.algomaze.control.solvers

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MazeSolver
    A MazeSolver takes a Maze as a parameter and returns a Stack containing Cells that comprise the solution to the Maze.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DijkstraMazeSolver
    Solves a given Maze using Dijkstra's shortest path algorithm.
    FibonacciHeap<E>
    The FibonacciHeap is a priority queue.
    FibonacciHeap.Node<E>
    The Node class is only used by the FibonacciHeap class to store the element supplied with the FibonacciHeap.enqueue(Object, double) method.
    FibonacciHeapTest  
    MazeSolverFactory
    The MazeSolverFactory class generates MazeSolver objects.
